Package editeur.model.commands

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICommand
    The interface ICommand represents the Pattern command.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CareTaker
    The type CareTaker : work with the Memento Pattern and Command Pattern, track the commands and add it to undo and redo vectors to further use.
    Command
    The type Command represents the Command Pattern and Work with Memento for undo-redo easily with preserved Encapsulation.
    CommandAdd
    The type CommandAdd add a shape to the source when executed, can be undone.
    CommandDelete
    The type CommandDelete delete the toDeleteShape from the source : can be undone.
    CommandGroup
    The type CommandGroup : can group into a composite and be undone.
    CommandMove
    The type CommandMove can move the source to position dx,dy : can be undone.
    CommandRecolor
    The type CommandRecolor can recolor the source and be undone.
    CommandRescale
    The type CommandRescale can rescale the source of factor times, can be undone.
    CommandRotate
    The type CommandRotate can rotate the source of factor angle and be undone.
    CommandRoundBorders
    The type CommandRoundBorders can make borders rounds if source is able to, can be undone.
    CommandUngroup
    The type CommandUngroup can ungroup a composite group and add it to source : can be undone.
